summary: Provides a main window interface for managing and displaying version history in the MSUI, handling user actions such as loading changes, previewing edits, undoing, refreshing, renaming, and deleting versions, as well as updating UI elements like lists, labels, and buttons.
business_intent: Facilitate collaborative version control by giving users an intuitive UI to track, compare, and manipulate different data versions, supporting efficient navigation, rollback, and organization of changes.
